QuestData.Title: Schematic Reassimilation: Deathrunner
QuestData.Description: <This schematic contains the pattern of a new protoform construct. Present it to an appropriate protoform forge and it may instantiate one of these creatures for you.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Present the schematic to an appropriate protoform forge.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Present the schematic to an appropriate protoform forge in Zereth Mortis.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent. With this schematic and the right components, a new song can begin here to accompany you.
